There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary—(1) $2,000,000 for fiscal year 2008; and

(2) $10,750,000 for each of fiscal years 2009 through 2012.

(Pub. L. 107–296, title VIII, § 899J, as added Pub. L. 110–161, div. E, title V, § 563(a), Dec. 26, 2007, 121 Stat. 2090.)</akn:p></akn:content><akn:subsection eId="subsec_488i_1"><akn:num>(1)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(1) $2,000,000 for fiscal year 2008; and</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_488i_2"><akn:num>(2)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(2) $10,750,000 for each of fiscal years 2009 through 2012.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection></akn:section></akn:body></akn:act></akn:akomaNtoso>